song.title: Lemurian Seafloot Apparatus
song.info:
Lemurian Seafloot Apparatus by noby, that would be the track title.
Made for the MS-Dos demo titled ''Mangareva''.
Cosmic metaphysical mythological production.
My first tracker module in over a year, probably the best I've done.
Respect and apologies to everyone whose samples I might have ripped.
Exploring Andrean sand dunes...
